\lim_{\tau\rightarrow \infty} \int_{-c/\tau}^0 e^{-\beta x}(\tau x+c)^{(\lambda/\tau) -1}dx
1/\lambda
y = \tau x + c
\frac{1}{\lambda}
y = \frac{\lambda}{\beta}
\tau \to \infty
 \frac{1}{\tau} \int_0^c e^{\frac{\beta}{\tau} (c - y)} y^{\lambda / \tau - 1} d y 
 \frac{1}{\lambda} c^{\lambda / \tau} + \frac{\beta}{\lambda \tau} \int_0^c e^{\frac{\beta}{\tau} (c - y)} y^{\lambda / \tau} dy 
s=\beta(x+\frac{c}{\tau})
